#: C/system-admin-guide.xml:25(para)
msgid ""
"The MATE Desktop implements menus according to the <ulink url=\"http://www."
"freedesktop.org/wiki/Standards/menu-spec\">XDG menu specification</ulink>. "
"By supporting this specification, MATE allows you to:"
